high_descs: walk to face counter to right of sink
pick up ladle from counter top
walk to the left to face counter top to left of sink
wash ladle in sink, pick up ladle
step back to face cabinets and drawers under sink
put ladle in bottom right drawer
anns.task_desc: put a washed ladle into a drawer

high_descs: Go to the counter in front of you, to the right of the sink.
Pick up the large spoon on the counter.
Go to the sink to your left.
Clean the spoon inside of the sink.
Turn around and move forward, then turn back around to face the drawers beneath the counter.
Beneath the counter adjacent to the sink, open the bottom left drawer and put the large spoon inside.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean large spoon inside the drawer.

high_descs: Turn right then turn left and go forward to the counter.
Pick up the large spoon from the counter.
Walk to the left then turn to the right to face the sink.
Place the large spoon in the sink and wash it . Take the spoon out of the sink.
Turn to the right and walk back the turn back to the left to face the shelves.
Open the bottom drawer and place the large spoon inside.
anns.task_desc: Wash a large spoon and put it away.
